The paper proposes a new method for uncertainty estimation and out-of-distribution detection in neural networks with softmax output. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
